data.description: WELCOME HOME!! Stunning 4-bedroom home on 2 lots in the heart of Channelview located on a corner lot!! This home as has it all with amenities and features to include a massive corner lot, beautiful wood bricked pillared corner fencing, a designated office, formal dining room, huge den, breakfast room, a sunroom/bonus room with access to the backyard, Perfect for entertaining and family. It is almost 1/2 an acre and a true must see!!
